data.description:
This charming home features a recent roof update, ensuring your peace of mind and protection from the elements. Nestled on a generous corner lot, this property offers a spacious backyard for all your outdoor activities and gardening dreams.

As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open kitchen layout, perfect for hosting gatherings and family meals. With a little bit of TLC and your personal touch, this kitchen can become the heart of your home.

The house boasts a versatile floor plan that provides you with endless possibilities for customization and modernization. Transform this space into your dream home, with ample room for your creativity to shine.

The backyard invites you to create your own oasis, whether it's a lush garden, an outdoor dining area, or a play area for kids and pets. The corner lot provides added privacy and space to roam.

This property offers a canvas for you to design a home that perfectly fits your lifestyle. With a solid foundation, a new roof, a spacious backyard, and an open kitchen, you have the basics covered, and it's time to let your imagination run wild and turn this house into your ideal haven.

In summary, this home is a hidden gem with enormous potential. With some updates, your personal touch, it can become the perfect place to create lasting memories. The combination of a spacious backyard and corner lot is a rare find and offers endless possibilities for those with vision and ambition.
